sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    actor NewUser
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Cache as Redis

    Note over Admin, Cache: Admin Login
    Admin->>FE: Enter email + password
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/login<br/>{ email, password }
    API->>DB: Fetch User by email
    DB-->>API: User document
    API->>API: bcrypt.verify(password, hash)
    API->>API: Sign JWT access token (15 min)
    API->>API: Generate random refresh token (32 bytes)
    API->>Cache: SET refresh:{hash} = user_id (TTL 7d)
    API-->>FE: { access_token, refresh_token }

    Note over Admin, Cache: Admin Generates Invite
    Admin->>FE: POST /admin/invite { email }
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/admin/invite
    API->>API: Require system_role == admin
    API->>API: Generate 32-byte random token
    API->>DB: Insert InviteToken { token_hash, email, expires_at }
    API-->>FE: { invite_url, expires_at }
    Admin->>NewUser: Share invite_url (copy-paste)

    Note over NewUser, Cache: New User Registration
    NewUser->>FE: GET /accept-invite?token=...
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/auth/accept-invite?token=...
    API->>DB: Find InviteToken by SHA-256(token)
    DB-->>API: InviteToken (validate: not expired, not used)
    API-->>FE: { email, expires_at }
    NewUser->>FE: Submit { display_name, password }
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/accept-invite
    API->>DB: Create User
    API->>DB: Mark InviteToken.used_at = now()
    API->>API: Sign JWT + generate refresh token
    API->>Cache: SET refresh:{hash} = user_id (TTL 7d)
    API-->>FE: { access_token, refresh_token }

    Note over NewUser, Cache: Silent Token Refresh
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/refresh { refresh_token }
    API->>Cache: GET refresh:{hash}
    Cache-->>API: user_id
    API->>API: Rotate: delete old, issue new refresh token
    API->>Cache: SET refresh:{new_hash} = user_id (TTL 7d)
    API-->>FE: { access_token, refresh_token }
